    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Scorching Ray</strong> (Level 2 Evocation)</p><p>You create three rays of fire and hurl them at targets within range. You can hurl them at one target or several.</p><p>Make a ranged spell attack for each ray. On a hit, the target takes 2d6 fire damage.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you create one additional ray for each slot level above 2nd.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 120 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
